summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of a portion of Calvary Cemetery, - Lots 13 and 14, Block 46, Boston Company's Plat - a portion of Lots 7 and 8, Block 16, Woodland Addition to Salmon Bay City - Lot 5, Block 9, McAleer's Supplement to Seattle Homestead Addition and Lot 2, Block 118, Gilman Park Addition, with respect to Use and Area Districts and amending Ordinance No. 45382 as amended by adding thereto two new sections, numbered 2-29 and 17-10.
